        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="scale" size={22} /></div>
        <h4>US Availability & Value (25%)</h4>
        <p>Can you reliably buy it on Amazon or at a US retailer? Is the import markup reasonable? Products with consistent stock and fair pricing scored higher than rare or overpriced imports.</p>
